# Apex -> canonical www host. Also enforced at the Cloudflare DNS level; keeping
# it here documents the intent and covers Pages preview domains.
https://ashwend.com/*  https://www.ashwend.com/:splat  301

# No SPA catch-all on purpose: the site is a single prerendered page, so an
# unknown path should fall through to Cloudflare Pages' 404 handling (the
# branded public/404.html) and return a real 404, not rewrite to the homepage
# with a 200 (which turns every bad URL into a soft 404 that search engines
# index as duplicate content).
